@ClientApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Получить всех клиентов
GET {{ClientApi_HostAddress}}/api/clients
Accept: application/json

###

### Получить клиента по ID
GET {{ClientApi_HostAddress}}/api/clients/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Добавить клиента
POST {{ClientApi_HostAddress}}/api/clients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Иван",
  "lastName": "Петров",
  "email": "ivan.petrov@example.com",
  "balance": 75000,
  "accountAgeDays": 400,
  "status": "Active",
  "hasOverduePayments": false
}

###

### Анализ клиента (вычисляемый ответ)
POST {{ClientApi_HostAddress}}/api/clients/analyze
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Мария",
  "lastName": "Сидорова",
  "email": "maria@example.com",
  "balance": 120000,
  "accountAgeDays": 500,
  "status": "Active",
  "hasOverduePayments": false
}

###
